{"tid":270735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四晚會】支聯會宣布11萬人參加燭光晚會","createTime":"2017-06-04T13:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T13:47:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d61d100935b2609145cab4043fc64efe2dbad90","tid":270735,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170604/s00001/817159a19a627366928ff0bc7958efdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170604%2Fs00001%2F817159a19a627366928ff0bc7958efdf.jpg&h=394b7f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天是六四28周年，支聯會於維園舉行燭光晚會，至晚上約9時40分，支聯會宣布約有11萬人參加晚會。<br />\n<br />\n在場不少巿民過去都曾到維園參加晚會，其中56歲的司徒小姐來足28年，她憶述六四當日身處海外，透過電視一邊流眼淚一邊收看現場情況。司徒小姐強調「28年好像仍然很近，有些事情我們是不可忘記」。對於有大學生表示不再參與或舉辦六四相關活動，司走小者稱感到心痛，認為「年輕人是未來的棟樑和希望」，加上有感氣氛已轉淡，憂慮市民會逐漸忘記六四事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170604/s00001/1496583613199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170604%2Fs00001%2F1496583613199&d=DKvAiAsYFaNpUWw8J7SPi7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=6cfa0999\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170604%2Fs00001%2F1496583613199&h=bd86410e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170604/s00001/1496583613199</a>"},{"pid":"2a883bb574e2a94a95bd747d0340744b680959e0","tid":270735,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}